gy and evolution of various salmonid species. To address these pressing issues, we collaborate with numerous state and federal agencies, non-profits, and tribal organizations.\r\n\r\nThe GVL is also an active training ground for a large number of young <a title=\"People\" href=\"http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/people/\" target=\"_blank\">scientists</a> at various stages in their careers, from high school students to graduate students to project scientists.','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2014-06-12 20:27:23','2014-06-12 20:27:23','',0,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/?page_id=30',0,'page','',0),(31,1,'2014-02-10 19:06:41','2014-02-10 19:06:41','','Home','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-v1','','','2014-02-10 19:06:41','2014-02-10 19:06:41','',30,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/?p=31',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2014-02-12 19:03:38','2014-02-12 19:03:38','','Ppl_Profile Picture Upload','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_ppl_profile-picture-upload','','','2014-02-21 18:10:35','2014-02-21 18:10:35','',0,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/?post_type=acf&#038;p=69',0,'acf','',0),(72,1,'2014-02-12 19:42:57','2014-02-12 19:42:57','','Ppl_Curriculum Vitae Upload','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_ppl_curriculum-vitae-upload','','','2014-02-21 18:10:26','2014-02-21 18:10:26','',0,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/?post_type=acf&#038;p=72',1,'acf','',0),(80,1,'2014-02-14 19:33:37','2014-02-14 19:33:37','','Mariah Meek','','publish','closed','closed','','mariah-meek','','','2014-03-20 17:33:33','2014-03-20 17:33:33','',0,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/?post_type=people&#038;p=80',0,'people','',0),(81,1,'2014-02-14 19:33:00','2014-02-14 19:33:00','','Mariah Meek Profile Image','','inherit','closed','open','','img_1612','','','2014-02-14 19:33:00','2014-02-14 19:33:00','',80,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/IMG_1612.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(82,1,'201