p;','98% Formamide Loading Dye','','inherit','closed','open','','307-revision-v1','','','2014-03-07 21:03:10','2014-03-07 21:03:10','',307,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/307-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(316,1,'2014-03-07 21:07:00','2014-03-07 21:07:00','<strong>For 100ml of storage buffer:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>50 ml Glycerol</li>\r\n	<li>1 ml 1M Tris-HCl pH 7.5</li>\r\n	<li>0.29g CaCl<sub>2</sub></li>\r\n	<li>ddH20 to 100ml</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>For 10 ml of Proteinase K stock solution:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Put 10ml of storage buffer in a 15ml screw-cap tube</li>\r\n	<li>Add 100mg of Proteinase K</li>\r\n	<li>Mix well by inverting until crystals are dissolved</li>\r\n	<li>Put 1ml aliquots into 1.5ml microfuge tubes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nStore at -20°C','Proteinase K','','publish','closed','open','','proteinase-k','','','2014-03-07 21:19:41','2014-03-07 21:19:41','',217,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/?page_id=316',0,'page','',0),(317,1,'2014-03-07 21:07:00','2014-03-07 21:07:00','<strong>For 100ml of storage buffer:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>50 ml Glycerol</li>\r\n	<li>1 ml 1M Tris-HCl pH 7.5</li>\r\n	<li>0.29g CaCl2</li>\r\n	<li>ddH20 to 100ml</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>For 10 ml of Proteinase K stock solution:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Put 10ml of storage buffer in a 15ml screw-cap tube</li>\r\n	<li>Add 100mg of Proteinase K</li>\r\n	<li>Mix well by inverting until crystals are dissolved</li>\r\n	<li>Put 1ml aliquots into 1.5ml microfuge tubes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nStore at -20°C','Proteinase K','','inherit','closed','open','','316-revision-v1','','','2014-03-07 21:07:00','2014-03-07 21:07:00','',316,'http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/316-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(318,1,'2014-03-07 21:08:00','2014-03-07 21:08:00','<strong>Buffers &amp; Stocks</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a title=\"98% Formamide Loading Dye\" href=\"http://localhost/~psalessi/Genetics_Lab/resources/protocols-and-procedures/98-formamide-loading-dye/\">Formamide Loadin